.TH "ssam_clear_controller" 9 "ssam_clear_controller" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ssam_clear_controller \- Remove/clear the main controller reference.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" ssam_clear_controller
.BI "(void "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "void" 12
no arguments
.SH "DESCRIPTION"

Clears the main controller reference, i.e. sets it to NULL. This function
should be called before the controller is shut down.
